# Invoke Specialist Reviewers

After non-trivial changes, invoke specialist reviewers. In Cursor, use the Task tool with
`readonly: true` and the appropriate `subagent_type` (e.g., `"code-reviewer"`).

See `.agent/directives/invoke-code-reviewers.md` for the full policy and reviewer catalogue.
